svg.text: Having a hard time gathering friends for a meal?
Difficulty deciding on a time and place?

g.text: Isra Sunhachawi - Xi Chen - Kirill Mangutov - Jonathan Park - Harrison Kiang - Andrew Borg

text.tspan: Meal times are special; we wanted
to share that time with our closest friends
We decided to build an app that would allow
users to quickly and easily gather their friends
Users navigated the app to create
a meeting and invite their friends
We have built an app that allows users to
communicate their availability in a visual way
The Timebar™ makes it easy for users to relay
their availability to their friends for meetups
Adding Facebook™ integration to the app would
allow users to more readily invite their friends
